					<description><![CDATA[ Read about the journeys three students took to their Dec. 10 graduation ]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>More than 1,900 University of Illinois Chicago undergraduate students and 1,300 graduate students will be celebrated during&nbsp;<a href="https://commencement.uic.edu/schedule-2/fall-commencement-ceremonies/">fall 2022 commencement ceremonies</a> Dec. 10.</p>
<p>&nbsp;Read about the journeys three of these students took to their UIC graduation:</p>



<div class="alignfull wp-block-ugb-image-box ugb-image-box ugb-e5057f9 ugb-image-box--v4 ugb-image-box--columns-3 ugb-image-box--design-captioned ugb-image-box--with-arrow ugb-image-box--align-center ugb-main-block"><style>.ugb-e5057f9 .ugb-image-box__box{border-radius:0px !important}.ugb-e5057f9 .ugb-image-box__item{height:325px !important}.ugb-e5057f9 .ugb-image-box__item1 .ugb-image-box__image{background-image:url(https://today.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Erica-Bhatti-590x393.jpg)}.ugb-e5057f9 .ugb-image-box__item2 .ugb-image-box__image{background-image:url(https://today.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/cc-hier-501x406.jpeg)}.ugb-e5057f9 .ugb-image-box__item3 .ugb-image-box__image{background-image:url(https://today.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Image-590x394.jpg)}.ugb-e5057f9 .ugb-image-box__item4 .ugb-image-box__image{background-image:url(https://today.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/112221_Amanda-Trevino_JC0060-590x393.jpg)}.ugb-e5057f9 .ugb-image-box__overlay-hover{background-color:var(--stk-global-color-11912,#3f2816) !important}.ugb-e5057f9 .ugb-image-box__item:hover .ugb-image-box__overlay-hover{opacity:0.7 !important}.ugb-e5057f9 .ugb-image-box__title{font-size:20px !important}.ugb-e5057f9 .ugb-image-box__description{text-align:center !important}.ugb-e5057f9 .ugb-inner-block{text-align:center}.ugb-e5057f9 .ugb-block-content{column-gap:0px !important}@media screen and (min-width:768px){.ugb-e5057f9.ugb-image-box{padding-right:35px !important;padding-left:0px !important}}@media screen and (min-width:768px) and (max-width:1025px){.ugb-e5057f9 .ugb-image-box__item{height:300px !important}}@media screen and (max-width:768px){.ugb-e5057f9 .ugb-image-box__item{height:300px !important}}</style><div class="ugb-inner-block"><div class="ugb-block-content"><div class="ugb-image-box__item ugb-image-box__item1 ugb-image-box__box ugb--shadow-0 ugb--hover-shadow"><div class="ugb-image-box__box ugb-image-box__image-wrapper"><div class="ugb-image-box__box u